
CTF Server

 Features
  - Executes exploits
  - Manages workers
  - Assigns exploits to workers
  - Manages schedule
  - Code Library
  - Library is pushed to workers
  - Network Monitoring (NM) on remotes / wireshark
  - Regex for automatic alerts in NM

 Requirements
  - Extensible! It must be flexible! Each CTF varies!
  - So: Every module should be configurable / plugable

 This semester
  - Integrate exploits for IoT devices
  - "Play with IoT": we bring it all together and try it
